#常见问题与解决方案
1、rviz报错无法打开
[ INFO] [1519612289.671282108]: rviz version 1.11.18
[ INFO] [1519612289.671330823]: compiled against Qt version 4.8.6
[ INFO] [1519612289.671345237]: compiled against OGRE version 1.8.1 (Byatis)
解决方案： 
1、rm -rf .rviz/
2、如1不行，则关闭TeamViewer,改用显示屏进行显示
